title: Can you see it? Res Lease in Austin. 2 Beds, 1 Baths
posting_body: ["Don't miss this gorgeous top floor, two bedroom condo in South Austin!", 'This unit features a sunny open concept layout, balcony off the living room & master bedroom, ceiling fans throughout, stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, fridge, W/D included, 1 reserved parking space in the gated garage, and more!', 'This community features a community pool, dog park, grill, and lounge area.', 'Stellar location right next to the new Easy Tiger and conveniently located near 360, Mopac, and 290.', 'Just moments away from great local shops and restaurants!', '**BONUS - Extra storage space available in the garage for an additional $100/month!', "** Don't let this one slip through your fingers!", 'Apply TODAY!', ' *** Send Text Message FEDERICO to', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Federico Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 8544450)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Matt Leschber, 1836 Realty & Property Mgmt']
